cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the design and implementation of a distributed deep learning platform, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also addresses the challenges of scalability and usability, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS). The platform is applied to multimedia applications, specifically image classification (cs.CV), and the paper discusses the use of deep learning models (cs.NE).
